          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "C. Plural definite as subject",
      "instructions": "A plural definite description is a type-e individual (the maximal sum). Apply it as a subject to a VP by FA ‚Äî the VP predicate holds of the entire sum, expressing a collective or distributive claim depending on the predicate.",
      "items": [
